      "id": "81c67a20_5aadae77",
      "file_path": "docker-compose/docker-compose.yml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 158,
      "message": "This causes docker to create a bind mount, which causes permission issues running in Linux.\nThere are 3 choices here:\n- docker volume\n- bind mount\n- tmpfs volume\nIf we want persistence, a docker volume would be the easier choice. Change to:\n  - grafana:/var/lib/grafana\n\nand add a volumes section to the end of the file:\n  volumes:\n    grafana:",
